article_title: Busted: Obamacare Co-Ops Are Underwater And Sinking Fast

og.description: Democrats inserted "co-ops" into Obamacare to prove that consumer-run nonprofit organizations could do a better job of providing affordable health insurance than private health insurers—and they've failed miserably.
